name: Light continues to echo three years after stellar outburst
description:
The Hubble Space Telescope's latest image of the star V838 Monocerotis (V838 Mon) reveals dramatic changes in the illumination of surrounding dusty cloud structures. 

Name:	V838 Mon
Type:	Milky Way : Nebula
Constellation:	Monoceros
Category:	Nebulae

3,629 editions for the known 3,629 planetary systems to date.
